# Keep line endings stable so the byte-exact bundle-freshness gate is deterministic
# across machines/editors (a Windows CRLF checkout or an editor re-adding a BOM would
# otherwise make the locally-built longwave-dev.html differ from CI's and trip the gate).
* text=auto eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.css  text eol=lf
*.js   text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.md   text eol=lf
